<HL>
   Stocks, Bonds Tumble as Oil Soars
   ---
   Wednesday's Markets:
   Dow Slumps 43.81
   As Broad Indexes Fall
   To 52-Week Lows
   ----
   By Christopher Winans
   Staff Reporter of The Wall Street Journal
</HL>
<DATE>
08/23/90
</DATE>
